These red leather gloves were designed with an arcane spellcaster in mind.  They allow for a more fluid cast of spells, and enhance the wearers agility as well.

The longbow is a refinement of the shortbow, designed to increase the range and power of an arrow strike. The stave portion of a longbow is nearly as tall as the archer, and can reach over six feet. This one has been designed to fire arrows at a higher velocity.
These are bagpipes, but there is nothing special about them.
